name: Sedan
description: Passenger cars with a three-box configuration offering comfort and fuel efficiency.

name: SUV
description: Sport Utility Vehicles designed for versatility, off-road capability, and spacious interiors.

name: Hatchback
description: Compact cars with a rear door that swings upward, providing convenient cargo access.

name: Coupe
description: Two-door sporty cars focused on performance and sleek design.

name: Convertible
description: Cars with retractable roofs, allowing open-air driving experiences.

name: Pickup Truck
description: Vehicles with open cargo areas designed for hauling and towing.

name: Van
description: Large vehicles ideal for transporting people or goods with ample storage capacity.

name: Crossover
description: Cars combining SUV features with a unibody platform for better comfort and fuel economy.

name: Electric
description: Vehicles powered entirely by electric motors and rechargeable batteries.

name: Hybrid
description: Cars combining internal combustion engines with electric propulsion for improved efficiency.
